  57,19,Those kred en DI His messengers est saints martyrs Rezerv them their Lord est their rekompenc their light As por those disbelieved rejected our revelations ili incurred Infer
  57,20,Kon this worldly life est ne plur than lud games kaj fanfaron vi hoarding de mon infan! Gxi est abund pluv produkt plant placx disbelievers! Tiam plant turn into useless fojn blov vent! En Hereafter tie est either severe retribution forgiveness el DI approval This worldly life est ne plur than temporary iluzi
