  57,27,Subsequent al them ni send our messengers. Ni send Jesus fil Mary ni don him Injeel (Gospel) ni ej kor de his followers kindness mercy. Ili invent hermitism ni neniam dekret them. All ni pet them do est uphold commandments aprob DI! Ili ne uphold message as ili hav. Consequently ni don those kred them their recompense while many da them est wicked
